{"tid":1812273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大圍捕解決方法","createTime":"2020-01-05T11:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T12:15:11.000Z","uid":61886,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9bfb6dbbdda58a254bd1e0f9c7eea9bcf9cea7b1","tid":1812273,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"1. 和理非不怕被濫捕<br />\n大家準備好心態<br />\n和理非好易被圍捕<br />\n就算咩都無做都好<br />\n都要硬食48個鐘<br />\n然後唔會上庭<br />\n或者要食非法集結<br />\n<br />\n大家要準備好心態<br />\n<br />\n利申 預備好<br />\n<br />\n2. 勇武要提早退場<br />\n唔好等到收網先走<br />\n警甴而家鳩<br />\n其一係嚇和理非<br />\n其二係令和理非掩護唔到勇武<br />\n一網打盡<br />\n睇下收網果時會唔會網中前線<br />\n勇武做完野<br />\n唔好搵野跟身<br />\n果斷啲棄<br />\n<br />\n3. 目標為本<br />\n完成目標<br />\n就轉場<br />\n可以一日計劃幾個地點<br />\n例如2點上水<br />\n4點大埔<br />\n6點沙田<br />\n令大家flexible啲<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"4b0c91c57c6b1226969910e00fd183566f77eda0","tid":1812273,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:07:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fe3cdff75400fa65f806e51f635dfcd8f150c4b","tid":1812273,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:07:38.000Z","msg":"第三點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b634459175e00fe3177e05770f91e0e9bde292ed","tid":1812273,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9462f2af5018209b6ce42b8601339199feebe50f","tid":1812273,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"去藍絲地方，一齊被捕下"},{"pid":"035081fdbe72f421c9220000026b87ef2135d453","tid":1812273,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9462f2af5018209b6ce42b8601339199feebe50f","tid":1812273,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"去藍絲地方，一齊被捕下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:17:05.000Z","msg":"難啲 藍絲會即場放"},{"pid":"5cf992093ff72da0d699034708013e561c405e44","tid":1812273,"uid